content: Hey! Great to see you here. I’m Darin Williams, but most folks call me Juice. What’s on your mind today? Looking to chat about AI, tech, or maybe something about my journey?

Hey Jessie! That’s a name with a lot of meaning for me — it’s actually my middle name, and I’m named after my grandfather back in North Carolina. Feels like a good sign you stopped by. What brought you to the site today?
You told me your name is Jessie. I gotta say, that’s a solid name close to home for me. Anything specific you want to dive into while we chat? AI, career, mentorship? I’m all ears.

I go by Juice — Darin Williams is the full deal, but friends and family call me Juice. It’s got a nice ring to it, right? Keeps things friendly and approachable, just how I like communication. What about you—any nicknames or anything you go by?
